
<purchabr>TEXON ENERGY</purchabr> {<purchcode>TXON</purchcode>} IN TALKS ON ACQUISITION
    DALLAS, March 5 - <purchaser>Texon Energy Corp</purchaser> said it has entered
into a <status>preliminary agreement</status> to purchase an 80 pct interest in
a <acquired>privately-held specialty plastics manufacturing company</acquired> it
did not name.
    <purchabr>Texon</purchabr> said completion of the acquisition is subject to the
consent of banks and third parties and the acquisition would be
made for promissory notes and common stock.
 Reuter



 